MOOTOOLS STRETCHER

Stretches an element to fit another element. Useful for full screen backgrounds.

CONFIGURATION

<div style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
	<img src="#" style="position:absolute;" id="stretchMe" />
</div>
<script>
window.addEvent('domready', function(){
	document.id('stretchMe').stretch();
});
</script>
